膠都打埋之前,要係度講清楚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母,而家係手足還拖</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係唔會主動攻擊途人,只有藍絲同黑警先會郁手打人先</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以,手足做野唔好阻撚住,唔係連你都打埋就無人想</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba56efa641768197934592295c164792a7a11fb2","tid":1550553,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Fc3EQi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Fc3EQi.jpg&h=df5a0fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmj2aWZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpmj2aWZ.jpg&h=a89d67f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31851ab52e1741c56aa7b08651283aad8874ace8","tid":1550553,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7fa36d41784613b2d8d1086582a8226efe1c62d8","tid":1550553,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:09.000Z","msg":"左膠再阻手足，打柒埋佢"},{"pid":"244ea1755be1007b1d958a4220e5632f14e